Notebook[{

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["Calculation of Colourless EPR for RnT^2", "Title",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.937551845952415*^9, 
  3.9375518562361727`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"dc16b9b3-bf85-4dd3-918d-\
dbacdba70c59"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Derivation of EPR to order \\nu^6. Comes from the term in the expansion of \
\\dot{S} of order \\nu^4. The correlator <x(t1)x(t2)x(t3)x(t4)> is evaluated \
to order \\nu^2 since it\[CloseCurlyQuote]s just OU when evaluated to order \
\\nu^0, so has zero cumulants above second order -> produces no music. The \
correlator <x(t1)x(t2)x(t3)x(t4)> consist of 2 diagrams at order \\nu^0,  15 \
diagrams at order \\nu^2 and more at order \\nu^4 which \
aren\[CloseCurlyQuote]t addressed here. (Gunnar has reasonable concern that \
some diagrams at O(\\nu^2) may be missing - this is completely possible, need \
to find a systematic way to make sure this isn\[CloseCurlyQuote]t happening).\
\n\nIn this notebook, the diagrams at O(\\nu^0) and O(\\nu^2) are evaluated \
and operated on by (d_t1+d_t2+d_t3+d_t4), and (d_t1d_t2d_t3 + d_t1d_t2d_t4 + \
d_t1d_t3d_t4 + d_t2d_t3d_t4) [note d_t1 = d/d_t1], corresponding to the terms \
that show up in the perturbative expansion of \\dot{S}. The sum is then \
integrated with the appropriate time-ordering to yield the EPR. \n\nFor the \
record - the key questions which need answering to flesh this out into a full \
analytic derivation are the following:\n- Why do all diagrams evaluate to \
zero under (d_t1+d_t2+d_t3+d_t4)?\n- Why do ",
 StyleBox["some",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " diagrams evaluate to zero under (d_t1d_t2d_t3 + d_t1d_t2d_t4 + \
d_t1d_t3d_t4 + d_t2d_t3d_t4) while some don\[CloseCurlyQuote]t?\n- Why do ",
 StyleBox["some ",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 "pairs of diagrams which are non-zero under (d_t1d_t2d_t3 + d_t1d_t2d_t4 + \
d_t1d_t3d_t4 + d_t2d_t3d_t4) sum to zero after this operation?\n- Why is it \
that one trio of diagrams which contain a Hermite index of 3 sum to zero \
under triple derivative operation?"
}], "Subtitle",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.937551871135159*^9, 3.937552026836239*^9}, {
  3.937552058428027*^9, 3.937552251819667*^9}, {3.937552289550569*^9, 
  3.937552742843196*^9}, {3.937641042312636*^9, 
  3.937641053588777*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"da795775-088d-4140-977f-\
c66fdd2321eb"],

